{
  "stem": "21786.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother, as I mentioned, was a very kind and very resourceful person.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was always there to help other people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she managed to-- whoever was in trouble, so always called on my mother.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I'm sure that she suffered terribly, the fact that she lost a daughter, and the circumstances under which she lost the daughter.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When I look at it from a distance, that wasn't really only compensation for something.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm sure that she was like that always.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The only thing she tried to persuade me, and tried to push a little bit, was me playing the violin.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I somehow liked music, but to train for hours was against somehow my principle of freedom.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was much easier to play hockey, or to play hooky or something similar.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But she had a gentle way of persuasion.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my father bought me a very beautiful instrument, which was an Italian instrument.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It wasn't a Stradivarius, or something similar.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But it was from the end of the 18th century.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I couldn't appreciate what's going on-- only when I lost-- when I had to give it away, then I realized.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I was pretty good already at that point.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I-- when Hitler marched in, I was capable to prepare for [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] beginning of the Brahms concerto.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But that was, my mother who was pushing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Then, when things got really tough, so-- she managed always to help people on the other side of the city, which was forbidden.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And she was willing to take off her-- the Star of David, and was willing simply to go and save somebody or bring something for somebody.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And finally when we were deported, I went with a different transporter.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
